function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	--mobs hostile
	for i, mob in ipairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_02_Cellar_Enemies")) do
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(mob, (Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_DEFAULT))
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(mob)
	end
	--deserter allied and run in 
	local deserter = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_02_Cellar_Deserter")[1]
	local marker = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_02_Cellar_Deserter_Fight")[1]
	Hydra.ActorSetTeam(deserter, (Hydra.TEAM_PLAYER_DEFAULT))
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(deserter)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(deserter, marker, "NPC_Run", false)
end

function Start()
	--stop ambient convo
	Hydra.CancelConversation(convCellar1)
	--do monk intro convo
	local monk = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_02_Monk")[1]
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convCellar3, monk)
	--deserter appears and approaches
	local deserter = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_02_Cellar_Deserter")[1]
	local marker = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_02_Cellar_Deserter_Walkto")[1]
	Hydra.ActorEnable(deserter)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(deserter, marker, "NPC_Walk", false)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(deserter, marker)
	--send guard kill event
	Hydra.EventSend("Penitent_02_Knight_Dead")
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	local deserter = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_02_Cellar_Deserter")[1]
	local marker = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_02_Cellar_Deserter_Exit")[1]
	local suna = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Penitent_02_Cellar_Suna")[1]
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(deserter, marker, "NPC_Run", false)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(deserter, 2)
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	--Hydra.TraceScreen("ACTOR ", suna, " PLAYING CONVO ", convCellar6)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convCellar6, suna)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(suna, marker, "NPC_Walk_Fast", false)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(suna, 2)	
end
